        <updateDate>2021-07-12T14:51:24Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Small Business Access to Recovery Capital Act</b></p> <p>This bill temporarily modifies the 7(a) Loan Guaranty Program of the Small Business Administration (SBA) by waiving borrower and lender fees, increasing the government guarantee to 95%, and increasing the maximum loan value to $10 million. The SBA must issue temporary COVID-19 guidance that reflects these changes.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
